Bio

I am a student at the Genomics Sciences program in the UNAM that has recently developed interests in different types of regeneration mechanisms in animals, yeast diversity in fermentative environments, epigenetics and proteomics.

Education

Undergraduate | Genomics Sciences - UNAM | August 2024 - Present |

Experience

Research stay in the Genome Evolution Laboratory at LIIGH-UNAM in isolating yeast species from agave fermentations in Mxico.
